==Demographics==
{{unreferenced section|date=July 2023}}
Lowgap's [[Zip Code Tabulation Area]] (Zip Code 27024) has a population of about 2,536 as of the [[United States Census, 2000|2000 census]].  The population is 51.9% male and 48.1% female.  About 96.5% of the population is white, 0.5% [[African-American]], 0.8% [[Indigenous peoples of the Americas|American Indian]], 1.1% [[Hispanic]], and 0.9% of other races.  0.7% of people are two or more races.  There are no native [[Hawaii]]ans or other [[Pacific Islander]]s.

The [[median household income]] is $32,404 with 13.3% of the population living below the [[poverty]] line.

